1
00:00:09,759 --> 00:00:11,344
Wasn't that a little rough today?

2
00:00:13,054 --> 00:00:15,765
Let me show you the rough love of a vampire

3
00:00:20,145 --> 00:00:22,814
- We'll see another total lunar eclipse tomorrow night

4
00:00:22,981 --> 00:00:26,693
- Large crowds have gathered
to witness the total lunar eclipse

5
00:00:48,214 --> 00:00:49,799
Minu

6
00:00:52,510 --> 00:00:54,095
Tomorrow...

7
00:00:55,472 --> 00:00:57,599
you're going back to where you came from, right?

8
00:01:05,356 --> 00:01:06,357
Should I just stay?

9
00:01:15,241 --> 00:01:16,659
No

10
00:01:17,827 --> 00:01:19,245
But...

11
00:01:21,873 --> 00:01:23,625
Promise me

12
00:01:26,169 --> 00:01:28,338
you'll come back

13
00:01:37,097 --> 00:01:38,723
I promise

14
00:01:39,474 --> 00:01:40,850
I'll come back

15
00:01:48,024 --> 00:01:49,859
Then that's all I need

16
00:01:50,568 --> 00:01:52,862
I trust you

17
00:01:55,615 --> 00:01:56,616
So then,

18
00:01:57,367 --> 00:01:59,536
should we have a little party tomorrow night?

19
00:02:01,454 --> 00:02:02,288
Sure

20
00:02:02,956 --> 00:02:05,834
Then I'll do the cooking

21
00:02:07,127 --> 00:02:08,128
Huh?

22
00:02:09,420 --> 00:02:10,463
No, no

23
00:02:11,214 --> 00:02:12,632
Let's just order delivery tomorrow

24
00:02:14,592 --> 00:02:17,220
Just kidding. I'll buy a cake

25
00:02:18,555 --> 00:02:19,430
Okay then,

26
00:02:20,515 --> 00:02:22,976
I'll come straight over as soon as my shift ends

27
00:02:24,602 --> 00:02:25,520
Sounds good

28
00:02:53,423 --> 00:02:56,843
I'll head out first, boss

29
00:03:40,845 --> 00:03:42,055
- Lucifer

30
00:03:42,513 --> 00:03:43,514
- No

31
00:03:43,973 --> 00:03:45,433
- Should I call you Jun?

32
00:03:47,268 --> 00:03:48,394
Luciel?

33
00:03:49,854 --> 00:03:51,397
- Just like a human,

34
00:03:51,731 --> 00:03:53,066
- you've got a thing for humans, huh?

35
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:54,984
You...

36
00:03:55,818 --> 00:03:56,819
Don't tell me

37
00:03:58,279 --> 00:04:00,531
What are you doing to Minu!?

38
00:04:01,658 --> 00:04:03,576
- You'd better get here fast

39
00:04:31,771 --> 00:04:32,355
Minu!

40
00:04:36,317 --> 00:04:37,277
Are you okay?

41
00:04:42,907 --> 00:04:45,868
I'm fine, but...

42
00:04:47,161 --> 00:04:48,121
Behind you...

43
00:04:48,288 --> 00:04:49,289
Huh?

44
00:04:52,667 --> 00:04:53,710
Watch out behind you!

45
00:04:58,965 --> 00:05:00,967
You have no idea
how long I've been waiting for this moment

46
00:05:01,926 --> 00:05:03,970
You think things will go your way
just because of this?

47
00:05:04,721 --> 00:05:06,556
I can do whatever I want,

48
00:05:07,181 --> 00:05:08,474
as long as you're out of the picture

49
00:05:21,863 --> 00:05:23,197
I saw it that day

50
00:05:24,907 --> 00:05:27,493
Your blood and his blood merging together

51
00:05:29,829 --> 00:05:30,705
And I knew

52
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,207
that I had finally found

53
00:05:34,042 --> 00:05:35,626
a way to destroy you

54
00:05:44,260 --> 00:05:46,095
Don't blame me for this

55
00:05:47,388 --> 00:05:48,806
You brought this on yourself

56
00:06:03,821 --> 00:06:06,282
Minu!

57
00:06:12,330 --> 00:06:13,539
Lucifer

58
00:06:14,624 --> 00:06:16,376
Bite me

59
00:06:22,590 --> 00:06:24,842
Now!

60
00:06:51,327 --> 00:06:54,122
You touched the one I cherished the most

61
00:07:09,345 --> 00:07:10,555
Die!

62
00:07:20,189 --> 00:07:21,232
Minu

63
00:07:21,691 --> 00:07:22,692
Are you okay?

64
00:07:30,867 --> 00:07:33,578
Thank you for everything, Lucifer

65
00:07:36,372 --> 00:07:37,874
Stop talking...

66
00:07:50,344 --> 00:07:51,846
I love you

67
00:07:53,890 --> 00:07:54,849
Lucifer

68
00:08:05,443 --> 00:08:07,069
You'll stay by my side, right?

69
00:08:12,825 --> 00:08:14,160
Yeah...

70
00:08:18,998 --> 00:08:20,583
Then that's all I need

71
00:08:48,277 --> 00:08:49,237
Minu

72
00:08:50,029 --> 00:08:52,031
Minu

73
00:09:43,165 --> 00:09:44,083
Jun!

74
00:09:56,846 --> 00:09:57,722
Minu

75
00:09:58,180 --> 00:09:59,932
What took you so long?

76
00:10:02,059 --> 00:10:03,394
Listen,

77
00:10:03,561 --> 00:10:05,104
the subway was delayed

78
00:10:05,104 --> 00:10:06,814
Stop lying, what do you mean?

79
00:10:06,814 --> 00:10:09,442
I'm serious, I rushed over
because I missed you so much

80
00:10:09,442 --> 00:10:10,568
What time did you even wake up?

81
00:10:25,499 --> 00:10:26,208
- That day,

82
00:10:27,585 --> 00:10:30,588
- I don't remember exactly what happened

83
00:10:31,964 --> 00:10:32,840
But what matters is,

84
00:10:33,674 --> 00:10:34,842
when I opened my eyes,

85
00:10:35,509 --> 00:10:36,552
right in front of me,

86
00:10:36,927 --> 00:10:37,845
Lucifer...

87
00:10:39,221 --> 00:10:39,847
No

88
00:10:40,473 --> 00:10:41,849
Jun was there

89
00:10:44,018 --> 00:10:44,852
And

90
00:10:46,771 --> 00:10:48,856
we are together at this moment

91
00:10:50,441 --> 00:10:55,071
Thank you so much
for watching Sweet Blood all this time
